Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來安樂岡同學最近有什麼進展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:22.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼突然問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:25.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺你最近都不和粟屋一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說是又想找我商量我才過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:31.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會講到我的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:35.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為安樂岡同學的話很有參考價值
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是俊男美女的情侶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,備受大家矚目哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:45.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以當然會在意你們怎麼樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:46.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:48.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 告訴我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:54.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們從暑假之後就沒見過面了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:57.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,十月都結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:04.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…感覺現在不見面會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:09.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是安樂岡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:10.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是成熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:15.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:16.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:27.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來皆川老師你意外地容易親近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:29.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:33.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正偽裝也沒用了 不裝了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:36.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在學校也這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:39.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼還要繼續呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:09.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這已經成了畢生的事業？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:17.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,景色真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那種事根本無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:23.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天風有點大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:27.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要盡快乾脆地搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是種怎樣的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:35.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:42.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:52.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:54.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:58.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要先休息一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:01.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:03.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:05.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我去倒水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:10.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反過來想想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說為什麼那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:20.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會變成那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:28.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就喝一口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我真的喝不了酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來 喝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:35.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一口乾 一口哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:45.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,酒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:53.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:08:00.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還記得 和母親來泡過一次溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:04.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,星星應該很美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜沒戴眼鏡 幾乎看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:10.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:12.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像做夢一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:15.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和皆川老師一起旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:19.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:21.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在房間裡一起看星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:29.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完 完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我總在關鍵時刻搞砸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:43.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明想和她一起看星星的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:49.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:55.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你眼鏡怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:58.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:03.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請你別笑 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:06.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是鮮花或是繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:09.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這世間一切美好的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都是為了比喻你而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得房間太暗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:20.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,暗才好 我想看月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼暗的話更加看不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你說「不用停下來」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:37.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:44.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不記得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡玩男人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是喜歡才做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:53.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不用停下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼被你說得像興趣一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:00.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然是因為喜歡才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的感受…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:10.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:15.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:16.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,需要想？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,需要想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:26.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我在緊張些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:27.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:28.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:30.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:32.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不希望你不討厭這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不討厭你 你就會討厭我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:42.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真丟臉 這什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,節奏全都亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:50.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:52.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:54.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還是喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:10:59.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,假如你喜歡的人討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:07.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你能否一直喜歡她呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:10.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分人都會說不吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一般來說 「喜歡對方」這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:22.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,往往包含了「對方也喜歡自己」的前提
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,無條件的喜歡別人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:28.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:30.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:32.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:37.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:38.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:45.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡我這種人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:02.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要說明喜歡的理由太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虧你還是個國文老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:11.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡的人能健康地活著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,聽起來像是真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:32.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:38.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個答案我還不滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:40.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不這麼覺得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我滿意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:52.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦產生了需求 便會永無止境
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欲望無法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:13:02.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣子總有一天 會傷害重要的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:09.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一定 並不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很渴望 很渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:14.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使傷痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:16.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那也一定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:20.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是特別的傷的話也足夠讓人變得堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:46.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼 舒服的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能 擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:55.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,身在其中的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,頭…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:08.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:11.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喝了這麼多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:17.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你該不會說自己斷片了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:35.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆…茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊是 名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:39.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:46.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和…和我結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:54.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,江山易改 本性難移
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我到現在也是充滿著算計
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:00.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個感情說不定也只是幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:08.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:12.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我會給你很多綠帽子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:20.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:22.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,綠帽子也行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:29.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還要去弄清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:34.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是否真的是幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人會改變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:44.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有人說不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:47.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:50.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等很久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:52.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:55.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厲害 像初次約會一樣的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:58.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是由俺 由我 由在下改變的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:02.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想看見被別人改變的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:04.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:00.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊 但是之前去過咖啡店了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:03.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊咧 約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:05.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哪會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:07.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑啦 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:15.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的約會也一定會成為 最後的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:22.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡高處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 讓人開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣從天空俯視大地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:30.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前的人們都做不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:34.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,曾發生過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:39.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到茜姐內心真正的聲音的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:43.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像喜歡教別人東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:44.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 不覺得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:52.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得的話也不會做這種打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:17:00.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢 想在死的時候也不留在任何人的記憶裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:03.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是反了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和正在做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:09.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,教師不是影響他人的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:15.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,成為老師的話 在大家的記憶中也不過一直是老師而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:19.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬間 感覺明白了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:24.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人 不把自己套在一些身份上就會不安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:27.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老師 女人 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望把這些身份背在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:32.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後局限於那個無聊的地方裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:37.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其實比誰都希望著自由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:41.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話 那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:42.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:45.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,將你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:52.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:55.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛的很高的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有同樣的理由喜歡它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:02.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難得現在有新的東西能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:05.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就想試試看那樣什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到的事增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:09.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣讓人感覺到自由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:11.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜歡那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:15.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:19.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:23.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我要將你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:24.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:31.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新的事情 做不到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:34.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我都想去嘗試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人能改變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:40.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,無論什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:43.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是被我而是被誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:47.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被僅有的一個命中注定 無可替代的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:52.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜姐已經不是老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:58.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是一個只想讓男人承認價值就滿足了的寂寞女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:02.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,終於擁有了名字與實體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那邁出新步伐的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,美得不可方物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:10.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊那什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多想要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:14.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:19.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:25.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:31.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那謝謝你了 送到這就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:36.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的是很喜歡小麥的臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得我是過分的傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:46.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得 但不會責怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:48.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:55.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一點也不溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:58.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會有責怪的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:00.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,結果我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對那個不軟弱不狡猾不是「女人」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:05.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就無法生存下去的那時候的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:07.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,充滿著愛慕而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:16.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:21.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 會一直記得的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:24.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,無論茜姐多想忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:25.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想要改變你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,改變前的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:38.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:40.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:43.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:45.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不會忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:51.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:19.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
